### Register
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "familyName": "Al-Bouz",
  "email": "admin@albouz.test",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@albouz.test",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Create person (replace <TOKEN>)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/people
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Mohamed",
  "last_name_raw": "Ben Ali",
  "notes": "From Tunis"
}

### PUT person (full replace)
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/v1/people/<PERSON_ID>
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "Mohamed",
  "last_name_raw": "Ben Ali",
  "notes": "Updated via PUT"
}

### Create edge
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/tree/edges
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromPersonId": "<PERSON1>",
  "toPersonId": "<PERSON2>",
  "type": "PARENT_OF"
}

### Get graph
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/tree/graph
Authorization: Bearer <TOKEN>
